      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "今日は野外イベントに来ていただいて\n本当にありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 96.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666666666714,
          "startTime": 96.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "私、サニーピースの川咲さくらっていいます！",
      "startTime": 98.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "今日はデビューしたステージでまたライブ出来るので\nすっごくワクワクしていました！",
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "私、このステージ大好きなんです！　風が気持ち良くて\n海も見えて、こんなに青空が広がって！",
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブに来てくれた方も、そうでない方も\n一緒に楽しんでくれたら嬉しいでーす！",
      "startTime": 121.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 766.6666666666657,
          "startTime": 122.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、いきますよー！",
      "startTime": 125.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3699.9999999999886,
          "startTime": 129.16666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n今日のライブ、どうでしたか……？",
      "startTime": 131.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "思いっきり楽しんでいる気持ちが\n観ている側にも伝わるようなステージだった",
      "startTime": 135.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ？　見てて分かっちゃうんですか？\nでもそうなんです。すっごく楽しかったです",
      "startTime": 141.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……良かったぁ\nそう言ってもらえると、凄く安心します",
      "startTime": 149.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.16666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんが応援してくれる声も、みんなと踊って\nステージを作り上げるのも、すごく新鮮な気持ちで……",
      "startTime": 156.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……ちょっと不思議ですね",
      "startTime": 161.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
